### Register user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login and copy token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Public endpoint should work
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Protected endpoint without token should fail with 401
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/me

### Protected endpoint with token should work
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin endpoint with USER token should fail with 403
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

